[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1449","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1449.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1281","title":"Breeze Network Server 远程系统重启漏洞","description":"Breeze Network Server 开发版中存在远程系统重启漏洞。远程攻击者可通过访问 configbreeze CGI 程序，向目标服务器发送特制请求，无需任何身份认证即可触发系统重启，导致目标服务中断。该漏洞影响 Breeze Network Server 开发版本，攻击条件简单，危害中等，建议升级至稳定版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1281"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.177","remediation":"Breeze Network Server 已停止维护，厂商未提供补丁。建议在 Web 服务器或反向代理层限制对 configbreeze CGI 脚本的访问（如通过 .htaccess 或 Nginx 拒绝规则），并在防火墙上仅允许可信 IP 访问该服务端口，或迁移至受支持的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11720","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1544","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1281.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1281","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1281.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1281.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-725f-7jxj-p6wv/GHSA-725f-7jxj-p6wv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87767/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1281.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1449.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1449.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1449.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1223","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1223.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0968","title":"BNC IRC代理 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BNC IRC代理软件2.2.4/2.4.6/2.4.8版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向代理服务发送特制的USER命令参数触发溢出，从而获取目标系统的控制权限。攻击无需身份认证，攻击者利用该漏洞可完全控制运行BNC代理的主机。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0968"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb","avd"],"published":"1998-12-26","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"升级BNC IRC代理至2.4.9及以上版本，或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。由于该漏洞年代久远且BNC项目已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的IRC代理软件如ZNC或IRC Proxy，并确保系统整体安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11711","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1927","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1546"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1223.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1447","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1447.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1278","title":"nlog CGI脚本系统命令注入漏洞","description":"nlog CGI 脚本未对 IP 地址参数中的 shell 元字符进行有效过滤，存在操作系统命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 nlog-smb.pl 或 rpc-nlog.pl 脚本发送特制请求注入恶意命令，在服务器上以 Web 权限执行任意系统命令。此漏洞影响使用 nlog CGI 脚本的配置环境，攻击无需认证，利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露或服务器被控制。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1278"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.807","remediation":"nlog 软件已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议立即从 Web 服务器 CGI 目录中移除 nlog-smb.pl 和 rpc-nlog.pl 两个脚本，或通过 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）访问控制规则禁止外部请求访问这两个 CGI 脚本。如需临时保留使用，必须修改脚本源码，在将 IP 地址参数传入 shell 命令前使用 Perl 的 quotemeta 函数或正则替换过滤 shell 元字符（; | & ` $() 等），禁止直接拼接用户输入到 system/exec 等系统命令调用中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91470326629357&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91471400632145&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1549","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1550","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1278.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1278","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1278.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1278.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcf8-4449-wvrr/GHSA-hcf8-4449-wvrr.json","https://github.com/digitalcoyote/NuGetDefense/blob/bc37c02051b7a7a9493a9628636fd2408ca3179c/Src/NuGetDefense/Program.cs","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87842/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1278.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1447.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1446","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1446.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1277","title":"BackWeb 客户端权限提升漏洞","description":"BackWeb 客户端在 Windows 注册表 Communication 键值中以明文存储代理认证的用户名和密码，本地攻击者可通过读取该注册表项获取敏感凭据信息，进而利用泄露的凭证提升自身权限，实现未授权访问。该漏洞影响 BackWeb 客户端软件，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，无需用户交互即可完成利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1277"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.690","remediation":"将 BackWeb 客户端升级至修复版本（如 v7.x 以上），或禁用代理认证密码存储功能。如无法升级，通过注册表权限管理工具限制 `HKLM\\Software\\BackWeb\\Communication` 键的读取权限仅为 SYSTEM 和 Administrators，移除普通用户的读取权限，防止密码泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91487886514546&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1565","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1277.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1277","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1277.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1277.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-76mc-rpwg-m8ch/GHSA-76mc-rpwg-m8ch.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87797/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1277.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1446.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0371","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0371.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0188","title":"Sun Solaris passwd 命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中的 passwd 命令存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 passwd 命令发送特制输入或触发异常状态，导致 passwd 进程崩溃或系统认证服务不可用，进而使得合法用户无法正常修改密码，影响系统正常运维。该漏洞影响多个 Solaris 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具备本地访问权限，利用条件相对有限，但成功利用后可能导致系统认证功能瘫痪。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0188"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.230","remediation":"建议升级到已修复此漏洞的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及以上补丁版本），或安装 Sun 提供的对应安全补丁。临时缓解措施可限制非授权用户对 passwd 命令的执行权限，或通过文件系统 ACL 控制 /usr/bin/passwd 的访问范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/182"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0371.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0290","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0290.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0139","title":"Sun Solaris x86 mkcookie 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris x86 系统中的 mkcookie 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序传递特製的参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的返回地址或函数指针，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris x86 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞提权至 root。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0139"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.823","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方安全补丁 106980-01 (Solaris 2.5.1) 或 106981-01 (Solaris 2.6)。如无法打补丁，立即移除 `mkcookie` 的 setuid root 权限：`chmod 0555 /usr/bin/mkcookie`，或直接删除该程序。限制本地普通用户登录受影响系统作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/8205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0290.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1450","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1450.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1282","title":"RealNetworks RealSystem G2 Server 信息泄露漏洞","description":"RealSystem G2 服务器将管理员密码以明文形式存储于全局可读的配置文件中，本地攻击者可通过读取该配置文件获取管理员权限。该漏洞影响 RealSystem G2 服务器版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，无需认证即可利用。由于密码以明文存储且文件权限设置不当，攻击者可轻易窃取管理员凭据，进而完全控制服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1282"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.293","remediation":"建议立即将包含管理员密码的配置文件权限改为仅管理员可读写（如 `chmod 600`），防止本地用户读取。同时升级到 RealSystem iQ 或更新版本，避免以明文存储密码。如无法升级，可考虑使用操作系统文件权限监控工具（如 Tripwire）检测配置文件的异常读取行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11543","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1542","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1282.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1282","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1282.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1282.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3wj4-jxxp-h483/GHSA-3wj4-jxxp-h483.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87841/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1282.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1450.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1445","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1445.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1276","title":"fte fte-console 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"fte 软件包中的 fte-console 组件在处理虚拟控制台设备时未能正确释放 root 权限，存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞，通过虚拟控制台设备获取 root 权限，进而完全控制系统。该漏洞影响 fte 0.46b-4.1 之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。默认配置下存在风险，需要本地访问权限才能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1276"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.560","remediation":"升级 fte 软件包至 0.46b-4.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 fte-console 未正确丢弃 root 权限的问题。如无法升级，可移除 fte-console 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/fte-console）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1998/19981207","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1609","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1276.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1276","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1276.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1276.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7p3-x2g8-59r3/GHSA-m7p3-x2g8-59r3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87752/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1276.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1998/19981207.data","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000401.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1445.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1361","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1361.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1147","title":"Platinum Policy Compliance Manager 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Platinum Policy Compliance Manager (PCM) 7.0 的 smaxagent.exe 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 Agent 服务端口（1827/TCP）发送超长字符串触发该漏洞，导致任意命令执行。攻击无需身份认证，可完全控制受影响系统，危害严重。受影响版本为 PCM 7.0，建议升级至最新版本修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1147"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-12-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:49.290","remediation":"联系 Platinum（后被 Computer Associates 收购）获取官方热修复补丁，升级至修复后的 PCM 版本。如无法升级，在防火墙或主机层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 1827，阻止外部向 smaxagent.exe 服务发送数据，以降低远程利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91273739726314&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/3164","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1430","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1147.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1147","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1147.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1147.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8vpv-fc53-gxvg/GHSA-8vpv-fc53-gxvg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88455/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1147.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/6833d28df9070f3a228f6256470bee59e545f901/advisories/2022/04/EUVD-1999-1128.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1361.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1154","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1154.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0798","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16271,\"outputTokens\":42,\"totalTokens\":16313}}","description":"bootpd（BOOTP 服务器守护进程）在 OpenBSD、FreeBSD 及 Linux 等操作系统上存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向运行 bootpd 服务的目标发送包含异常构造的 header type 字段的特制数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，从而可能执行任意代码或导致服务崩溃。该漏洞影响提供 BOOTP/DHCP 服务的系统，攻击者无需凭据即可在远程发起利用，危害严重。建议系统管理员升级至已修复该漏洞的最新版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0798"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-12-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.793","remediation":"立即为受影响系统应用安全补丁：OpenBSD 2.4 用户请升级至 OpenBSD 2.5 或应用 1998 年 11 月 28 日发布的 bootpd.patch（ftp://ftp.openbsd.org/pub/OpenBSD/patches/2.4/common/bootpd.patch）；FreeBSD 用户请升级至最新安全分支并更新 bootpd 端口；Linux 发行版用户请通过包管理器更新 dhcp/bootp 相关软件包。如无需 bootpd 服务，可直接在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 bootps 行并重启 inetd，或在防火墙层面禁用 UDP 67/68 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91278867118128&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0798.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0798","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0798.md","https://github.com/anchore/nvd-data-overrides/blob/404b484bd5d19c483528cbf4559074858313076b/data/1999/CVE-1999-0798.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ghpg-95cp-r25j/GHSA-ghpg-95cp-r25j.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0798.json","https://github.com/fosslight/fosslight/blob/4b9c95f462f87d3bb7703c29e88e9330275b06c4/migration/migration/scripts/20241104111630_update_v2.1.0_update_license_data.sql"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1154.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1448","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1448.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1280","title":"Hummingbird Exceed 敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Hummingbird Exceed 6.0.1.0 版本错误地捆绑了仅用于开发和测试的 DLL 组件，该组件会将用户登录凭据（用户名和密码）以明文形式记录到 test.log 文件中。本地攻击者可通过读取该日志文件获取敏感凭据信息，进而提升权限或横向移动。该漏洞影响 Hummingbird Exceed 6.0.1.0 及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商未提供官方补丁，建议用户删除或限制对 test.log 文件的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1280"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.053","remediation":"删除 Hummingbird Exceed 安装目录下随附的开发测试 DLL 文件，并清除所有已生成的 test.log 文件，确保敏感凭据不被明文记录。升级到 Hummingbird Exceed 6.0.2 或更高版本，该版本已移除此开发组件。如无法升级，通过文件系统 ACL 限制 test.log 的访问权限，仅允许管理员读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11512","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1280.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1280","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1280.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1280.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w9jw-rh3j-q667/GHSA-w9jw-rh3j-q667.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87850/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1280.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1448.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1182","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1182.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0836","title":"SCO UnixWare uidadmin 本地符号链接权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.0/7.0.1/7.1/7.1.1 系统中的 uidadmin 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在运行时会以 root 权限处理用户可控的文件路径，攻击者可通过创建指向敏感系统文件（如 /etc/passwd）的符号链接，诱使 uidadmin 以 root 身份写入或覆盖目标文件。攻击条件为本地普通用户账户，利用门槛低，成功后可获得 root 权限，造成系统完全沦陷。此漏洞由 symlink 竞争条件引发，属于典型的本地提权类安全问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0836"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-12-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 SCO UnixWare 7.1.3 或更高版本（已修复该 symlink 漏洞）；若无法升级，立即移除 uidadmin 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/uidadmin），并限制普通用户对 /var/opt/K/SCO/UnixWare/ 目录的写入权限，防止本地提权利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/842","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=19991202160111.20553.qmail%40nwcst282.netaddress.usa.net","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19654"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1182.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1182.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1182.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1202","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1202.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0869","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 框架欺骗漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 3.x 至 4.01 版本存在框架欺骗漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，在受信任网站的框架中插入任意内容，从而实施钓鱼攻击或信息欺骗。该漏洞利用浏览器同源策略的缺陷，无需用户交互即可触发，影响 Windows 平台上的 IE 浏览器用户，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0869"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.603","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.5 或更高版本以修复框架欺骗漏洞。该漏洞在 IE 5.5 及后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，建议禁用 Active Scripting 功能，或更换为现代浏览器（如 Edge、Chrome）以彻底规避风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-020","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19662","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0869.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0869.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0869","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0869.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0869.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c3g4-j4mv-jc79/GHSA-c3g4-j4mv-jc79.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0869.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1202.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1202.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1202.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0718","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0718.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0463","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 fcagent 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统中的 fcagent 组件存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络向目标系统发送特制请求，利用 fcagent 处理异常输入时的缺陷，导致该服务进程崩溃或系统资源耗尽，从而使系统无法正常提供服务。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。目前厂商已停止支持该版本系统，建议用户升级至受支持版本或采取网络访问控制措施进行缓解。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0463"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.940","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 安全公告 19981201-01-PX 提供的补丁，升级 fcagent 组件至修复版本。如无法打补丁，在防火墙或网络层面限制对 fcagent 服务端口（默认 8888/TCP）的访问，仅允许可信来源连接。鉴于 IRIX 6.4 已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0463.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0463","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0463.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0463.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-gxx9-6c3j-p4rc/GHSA-gxx9-6c3j-p4rc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0463.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82847/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0718.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0561","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0561.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0342","title":"Linux PAM 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux PAM（可插拔认证模块）存在不安全的临时文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在/tmp目录下创建符号链接指向目标文件，诱导使用了共享库的PAM模块在提升权限的过程中读写临时文件，从而利用条件竞争漏洞覆盖系统关键文件或执行任意代码，最终获取root权限。该漏洞影响多种Linux发行版及使用了PAM模块的UNIX类系统，攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，CVSS评分6.2，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0342"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.490","remediation":"建议升级 Linux PAM 至 0.64 及以上版本，该版本已修复临时文件竞争条件漏洞，改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件。旧版 Red Hat Linux 用户应安装 RHSA-1999:013 公告对应补丁。如无法升级，可限制不可信用户的本地登录权限，并启用严格的 umask 策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0342"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0561.toml"}]